uninstall:
- all others files of enb
- All injector
And others Mods like imaginator.

How to install;

Download the v0.139 series
place the .dll to the main folder of skyrim (wrapper version from enb)
place the enb from my folder to the main directory of skyrim


[url=http://www.enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0139.htm]ENBSeries v0.139[/url]

done, keep in mind if you use already a ENB then do a backup.

-----------------

Skyrim ( lol )

Intel (R) Core(TM) i5-2500 CPU @3,3Ghz (3,7Ghz overclocked)
